    "description": "Nature's Basket invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Senior Software Engineer at our Rajkot location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Nature's Basket:\nNature's Basket is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nature's Basket!",
